<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id799d4f21-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s2611"><num value="2611">§ 2611.</num><heading> Purposes</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The purposes of this chapter are to encourage—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id799d4f22-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s2611/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> conservation of energy supplied by electric utilities;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id799d4f23-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s2611/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> the optimization of the efficiency of use of facilities and resources by electric utilities; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id799d4f24-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s2611/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> equitable rates to electric consumers.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id799d4f25-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/617/tI/s101">Pub. L. 95–617, title I, § 101</ref>, <date date="1978-11-09">Nov. 9, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3120">92 Stat. 3120</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id799d4f26-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id799d4f27-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id799d4f28-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this title”, meaning title I (§ 101 et seq.) of <ref href="/us/pl/95/617">Pub. L. 95–617</ref>, <date date="1978-11-09">Nov. 9, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3120">92 Stat. 3120</ref>, which enacted subchapters I to IV of this chapter and <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s6808">section 6808 of Title 42</ref>, The Public Health and Welfare, and amended sections 6802 to 6807 of Title 42. For complete classification of title I to the Code, see Tables.</p>
</note>
</notes>
